      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The staff has 10 charges. It can expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells (save DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">12</span>): @spell[cone of cold] (5 charges), @spell[fog cloud] (1 charge), @spell[ice storm] (4 charges), or @spell[wall of ice] (4 charges). It regains [[/r 1d6 + 4]] expended charges daily at dawn. If the staff expends its last charge, roll a [[/r d20]]. On a 1, the staff turns to water and is destroyed.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
